fig. 5 G
). Projections of inferior layer of ventral rim subtriangular, apex spatulate placed laterally to segment X (fig, 5 G ). Median third of ventral rim slightly emarginated forming a shallow, narrow aperture covering the lateral portions of segment X (
fig. 5 J
). Carinae continued from the conical projection of inferior layer inconspicuous (
fig. 5 J
